BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SJ - Gretzky Hour Admission (25-26)
DTSTART:20260428T001500Z
DTEND:20260428T014500Z
DESCRIPTION:This Stick  Puck hour is designed for players to just skate an
 d work on any aspect of hockey he or she desires. And most importantly to 
 have fun! Each player is required to sign in before each session at front 
 desk to recieve wristband/sticker. Full USA Hockey Certified equipment req
 uired.Locker Rooms are Coed\, please plan accordingly. Scrimmages or small
  area games are not allowed! Advanced registration is requiredLimit 40 ska
 ters and 4 goalies. All Gretzky Hours after 9pm will only be available for
  online registration. No in person registration.No Refunds.
LOCATION:1500 South Tenth Street\, San Jose\, CA 95112
URL:https://apps.daysmartrecreation.com/dash/x/#/online/sharks/event-regis
 tration
END:VEVENT
